"slug": "missing-translation", "storyline": "Missing Translation is a simple yet oddly bizarre and charming story about a man (or woman depending on your preference) that seems to be living a boring and un-flavorful life, that is until they are transported to a mysterious world. In this world your selected character is to solve puzzles and do various tasks to further the plot.", "summary": "Missing Translation is a simple puzzle game that is quite interesting in the way it presents itself. There are no tutorials, it allows for that special sort of exploration that many gamers love. There is no text dialogue or vocal dialogue, it is simply a game that can be enjoyed by anyone regardless of their language. Missing Translation is a beautiful experience both visually and emotionally, with a fantastic soundtrack, and a great art style.", "themes": [{"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/missing-translation", "videos": [{"id": 8078, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "NcrJoWwMV_o", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NcrJoWwMV_o", "title": "Missing Translation Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NcrJoWwMV_o/maxresdefault.jpg"}]}